paragraphs.text:
%psql.sql

insert into vdwh_pol select * from hcatalog.cas.vdwh_pol

%psql.sql


create table vdwh_pol_tran1 as select agt_code, sum(prem_paid_total) from vdwh_pol group by agt_code

%hive 


create table cas.vdwh_pol_tran1 AS 
select agt_code, sum(prem_paid_total) from cas.vdwh_pol group by agt_code
